messages.msgSnippet: With wasps and yellow jackets, the queen leaves the nest before cold weather sets in.  The workers feast on anything before the frost.  Also their primary diet
messages.messageBody:
With wasps and yellow jackets, the queen leaves the nest before cold
weather sets in. The workers feast on anything before the frost. Also
their primary diet consists of other bugs, moths, caterpillars, etc.
Lisa of Montana
